<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Beauty Bliss - Product Promotion</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        height: 100vh;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #222222;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a800ff, #ff00c8);
      }

      a {
        color: #d55fbb;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #1e1e1e;
        padding: 30px;
        color: #f086d9;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 14px;
        background-color: #f4f3f3;
        min-height: 70vh;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #1e1e1e;
        padding: 14px;
        color: #d55fbb;
        text-align: center;
      }

      img {
        padding: 24px;
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
      }

      .product-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: space-around;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .product-item {
        background-color: #fff;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        padding: 15px;
        width: 45%;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
      }

      .product-item img {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .product-item h3 {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .product-item p {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #555;
      }

      .product-item a {
        background-color: #d55fbb;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <img
          src="cid:logo"
          height="120"
          width="120"
          alt="D' Plush Choice Logo"
          style="
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(168, 0, 255, 0.15);
            background: #fff;
          "
        />
        <h1 style="color: #a800ff; margin-top: 10px">
          Featured Product Promotions
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div
        class="email-body"
        style="
          border-radius: 16px;
          box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(255, 0, 200, 0.08);
          margin-top: -30px;
        "
      >
        <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #a800ff; font-weight: 600">
          We are thrilled to introduce some of our featured beauty products just
          for you. These products are carefully selected to enhance your beauty
          routine and provide you with the best results.
        </p>

        <div class="product-list">
          <% products.forEach(function(product) { %>
          <div
            class="product-item"
            style="
              background: #fff;
              border-radius: 8px;
              box-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(168, 0, 255, 0.07);
              padding: 10px;
            "
          >
            <img
              src="<%= product.img %>"
              alt="<%= product.name %>"
              style="
                border-radius: 8px;
                box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(255, 0, 200, 0.1);
                margin-bottom: 10px;
              "
            />
            <h3 style="color: #a800ff; margin-bottom: 10px">
              <%= product.name %>
            </h3>
            <p style="color: #222; margin-bottom: 20px">
              <%= product.description %>
            </p>
            <a
              href="<%= product.link %>"
              style="
                background-color: #ff00c8;
                color: #fff;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                border-radius: 5px;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-weight: 600;
              "
              >Shop Now</a
            >
          </div>
          <% }) %>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 17px; color: #a800ff; font-weight: 600">
          Stay tuned for more exclusive offers and beauty tips. Thank you for
          being a part of D' Plush Choice!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>&copy;2025 D' Plush Choice. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
